 222:src/main.cpp  **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 5: screaming aggressive lead ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 223:src/main.cpp  **** //   Detuned sawtooth stack (root + a hair-sharp twin + octave) for a thick,
 224:src/main.cpp  **** //   buzzing supersaw bite, pushed up into a cutting register. Heavy drive and a
 225:src/main.cpp  **** //   very high filter resonance make the cutoff whistle and scream as pressure
 226:src/main.cpp  **** //   sweeps it wide open. Finger-2 pressure piles on ring-mod + wavefold for
 227:src/main.cpp  **** //   extra snarl. Loud and nasty ŌĆö the output soft-clip keeps it from blowing up.
